import React,{useState} from "react"; function Login(){ const[text,setText]=useState( {login:"", password:"", phone:"", name:"", surname:""}, ) console.log(text) return(
setText({ ...{name:event.target.value}})}> setText( {...{surname:event.target.value}})}>
setText( ...{phone:event.target.value})}> setText( ...{login:event.target.value})}> setText( ...{password:event.target.value})}>
) } export default Login
